  <brief_title>Preoperative Chemoradiotherapy Combined With Nimotuzumab for Cervical Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Preoperative Concurrent Chemoradiotherapy Combined With Nimotuzumab Injection for Locally Advanced Cervical Cancer: a Phase II Study</official_title>
