  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the feasibility and efficacy of preoperative
      nimotuzumab injection combined with concurrent chemoradiotherapy for initially inoperable,
      locally advanced cervical cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
